messages.content:
This is a missed-optimization in InstCombine.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i1 @test_fcmp_ord_select_fcmp_oeq_var_const(double %x) {
  %cmp1 = fcmp ord double %x, 0.000000e+00
  %sel = select i1 %cmp1, double %x, double 0.000000e+00
  %cmp2 = fcmp oeq double %sel, 1.000000e+00
  ret i1 %cmp2
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i1 @test_fcmp_ord_select_fcmp_oeq_var_const(double %x) {
  %1 = fcmp oeq double %x, 1.000000e+00
  ret i1 %1
}

```
